                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner into custody. He said he bought the things six days before, and afterwards said it was six weeks since.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I said I bought them four weeks ago.</p>
